要留意返<br />\n買大啲嘅<br />\n太細嘅話會唔夠用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"Ok,我會俾心機養"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T07:52:43.000Z","msg":"呢份兩棲及爬蟲協會教養草龜嘅資料應該幾啱你<br />\n算係簡單咁介紹咗飼養重點<br />\n我嗰時初學養巴西龜<br />\n除咗睇書之外<br />\n就係睇呢個協會啲資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.hkherp.org/document/caresheet/Chinemys_reevesii.pdf&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiL6Y6K-4feAhWK7GEKHa9bDMcQFjAAegQICBAB&amp;usg=AOvVaw2rYkyRJyFZyVM8nRSAhLCc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkherp.org%2Fdocument%2Fcaresheet%2FChinemys_reevesii.pdf%26ved%3D2ahUKEwiL6Y6K-4feAhWK7GEKHa9bDMcQFjAAegQICBAB%26usg%3DAOvVaw2rYkyRJyFZyVM8nRSAhLCc&d=TqJSYLXMWS6ujcf1pnLk0P9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=7de52ae3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.hkherp.org/document/caresheet/Chinemys_reevesii.pdf&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiL6Y6K-4feAhWK7GEKHa9bDMcQFjAAegQICBAB&amp;usg=AOvVaw2rYkyRJyFZyVM8nRSAhLCc</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T09:00:34.000Z","msg":"多謝你先，我會俾心機養"},{"pid":"ebf5feaa843cfc8afdce9c05d7a2fcc449e1621f","tid":861941,"uid":7861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40e7569f175ff8a7949ffc30bc2db998f5685dc9","tid":861941,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21b5fb9a3fafac3879dbbba6a0fdda99fb5b42b3","tid":861941,"uid":7861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c7b75148087d87fc5ebaa45d122e9bf71ed9f16","tid":861941,"uid":3028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T07:49:13.000Z","msg":"放佢去公園龜池啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T07:50:18.000Z","msg":"我同佢咁有緣份，唔想離開佢"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"咁要對佢好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n養龜唔係想像中咁易<br />\n<br />\n分享下我隻龜個setting<br />\n可以參